      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/49031394-the-mothers">Quotes from The Mothers</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Grief was not a line, carrying you infinitely further from loss. You never knew when you would be sling-shot backward into its grip. —&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/7976992-grief-was-not-a-line-carrying-you-infinitely-further-from">87 likes</a>
